Didn’t have the pear so I used 0.25 Vta pear halves just to add the vibe but to not disrupt tams original recipe.&#xD;
&#xD;
I’m fond of the strawberry watermelon combo so this appealed to me, it’s a lovely mix, of I could change one thing I would swap the strawberry gummy and watermelon candy percentages around but that’s subjective because I like the strawberry to peep over the watermelon. 5 star mix if I ever tasted one :) good job tam, one day I’ll let you take ownership of the jammy berry title ❤️
